vanitygen
------------------------------------------
Standalone command line vanity address generator

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libOpenCL1-2.3.5-1
  libcurl4-8.20.0-1
  libpcre1-8.45-1
  libssl1.0-1.0.2u+za-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libOpenCL-devel-2.3.5-1
  libcurl-devel-8.20.0-1
  libpcre-devel-8.45-1
  libssl1.0-devel-1.0.2u+za-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/samr7/vanitygen

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/samr7/vanitygen/archive/0.21.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack vanitygen-0.21-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./vanitygen-0.21-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/vanitygen-0.21-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vanitygen-0.21-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(vanitygen)
  /usr/bin/keyconv.exe
  /usr/bin/oclvanitygen.exe
  /usr/bin/oclvanityminer.exe
  /usr/bin/vanitygen.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/vanitygen.README
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen/CHANGELOG
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen/README

------------------

